for (int value : arr)
{
  if (max < value)
  {
    max = value;
  }
}
```

II.
```java
int max = 0;
boolean first = true;
for (int value : arr)
{
  if (first)
  {
    max = value;
    first = false;
  }
  else if (max < value)
  {
    max = value;
  }
}
```

III.
```java
